create table user_account
(
open_id varchar(50) not null,
available_amount integer,
frozen_amount integer,
is_locked integer comment '0 未锁定 1 锁定',
out_amount integer,
in_amount integer,
create_time timestamp,
modify_time timestamp,
primary key (open_id)
);
